    <div class="container">
      <div class="bg-faded p-4 my-4">
        <hr class="divider">
        <h2 class="text-center text-lg text-uppercase my-0">Peru</h2>
        <hr class="divider">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-6"> <img class="d-block img-fluid w-100" src="img/peru.jpg"
              alt="">
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <p></p>
            <p>Peru is a smaller country in South America. Although it's
              smaller, there are many activities to be done. Below is a
              suggested activity to do while in Peru.</p>
            <p></p>
            <b>Hike Machu Picchu</b>
            <p></p>
            <b>Price of activity:</b> $$$ <br>
            <b>Name of hotel/hostel:</b>Pirwa Hostel Machu Picchu <br>
            <b>price of Hotel/hostel:</b> $$ <br>
            <b>Safety of location: </b> Very safe <br>
            <p></p>
            <p><b>Notes:</b> Machu Picchu will be a highlight of your trip! It
              is a beautiful hike and view to see. The hostel listed above is in
              a great location to Machu Picchu. It is a very affordable price as
              well.</p>
            <p><b><br>
              </b></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="bg-faded p-4 my-4">
        <hr class="divider">
        <h2 class="text-center text-lg text-uppercase my-0">Ecuador</h2>
        <hr class="divider">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-6"> <img class="d-block img-fluid w-100" src="img/amazon.jpg"
              alt="">
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <p><br>
              Ecuador is another small South American country. It is located
              right on the equator (that is how it gets its name). Ecuador is on
              the coast so it allows an individual to have a beach vacation. The
              amazon jungle also extends into Ecuador which allows for a hiking
              adventure too. Below is a suggested activity to do in Ecuador. </p>
            <p></p>
            <b>3 day tour of Amazon rain forest</b>
            <p></p>
            <b>Price of activity:</b> $$$$ <br>
            <b>Name of hotel/hostel:</b> Yacuma Ecolodge <br>
            <b>price of Hotel/hostel:</b> $$$$ <br>
            <b>Safety of location: </b> Risks of plants/ animals in Amazon rain
            forest <br>
            <p></p>
            <p><b>Notes:</b> Although this trip is rather expensive, it allows
              you to see the Amazon rain forest while on a guided tour. The
              price of the excursion and lodging is combined. Activities include
              hiking and canoeing while sightseeing. While in Ecuador, note that
              the public bus system is very unreliable and you should give
              yourself lots of time to get from place to place. </p>
            <p><b><br>
              </b></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
