            <p></p>
            <b>Visit Rio de Janeiro</b>
            <p></p>
            <b>Price of activity:</b> $$$ <br>
            <b>Name of hotel/hostel:</b>El Misti Hostel Rio - Copacabana <br>
            <b>price of Hotel/hostel:</b> $ <br>
            <b>Safety of location: </b> Although it is a large, busy city,
            tourists should be aware of potential theft.<br>
            <p></p>
            <p><b>Notes:</b> There are many sightseeing tours available in Rio
              de Janeiro. Rio de Janeiro also offers beaches and great
              nightlife. It is a "must-visit" when backpacking through South
              America.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
